@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xxrofv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.abs(wp.abs(v0 + 0.76)))
    v1 = (wp.sin(v1) + (tmp + wp.cos(v2 + 0.68)))
    tmp = v1
    v2 = wp.abs((wp.abs(v2 + 0.69) - (tmp + 0.64 - v0 + 0.20)))
    tmp = (v2 / wp.sin((tmp + 0.93 - v0 + 0.65)))
    v1 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
